isappointments in the short-term. I think this will have index-level impacts. I'm out for a couple months, then heavy back into photonics/neuromorphic/ARM, and the usual solid moat companies."}}}, "rest_id": "2069162068885098667", "source": "<a href="https://mobile.twitter.com" rel="nofollow">Twitter Web App</a>", "unmention_data": {}, "views": {"count": "14", "state": "EnabledWithCount"}}

